<h2>Wood Sunrooms</h2>
Nothing can beat the warmth and grace of a warm natural wood interior in your sunroom. Solar Innovations¬Æ offers a wide variety of options in wood sunrooms to create a summer feel all year round. Whether you want traditional or modern, Solar can customize all wood interior panels¬†to match existing architectural elements on your house.

Thermal efficiency tends to be higher with a wooden structure because wood allows for lower U-values. The lowered U-value means that the room will maintain a more even temperature and will not lose as much heat in the cold winter months. All of Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> systems are thermally isolated which prevents the metal frame from touching the glass at any point.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_single_image image="39057" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_column_text]
